            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3b0003-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:09:36.108+09:00">孙子说：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:09:43.65+09:00">战争，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:09:47.907+09:00">是国家的大事，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:09:53.95+09:00">它关系到民众的生死、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:10:01.038+09:00">国家的存亡，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:11:52.035+09:00">是不能不认真考察研究的。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:12:27.469+09:00">是不能不认真考察研究的。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:12:45.507+09:00">所以，应以如下五个方面的因素为纲领，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:13:09.489+09:00">把敌对双方的条件加以比较、估算，然后推测可能出现的结局。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:13:18.168+09:00">这包括：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:13:49.243+09:00">二天时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:13:56.416+09:00">三地利，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:14:03.945+09:00">四将帅，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:14:17.154+09:00">五法制。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:14:29.239+09:00">所谓政治，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:14:41.205+09:00">讲的是要民众与国君的意愿相一致，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:14:55.45+09:00">能够为国君而死、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:15:07.93+09:00">为国君而生，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:15:17.523+09:00">而毫不畏惧战争的危险。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:15:30.843+09:00">所谓天时，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:15:38.334+09:00">讲的是昼夜、晴雨、严寒、酷暑等气候和时令的变化。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:16:07.719+09:00">所谓地利，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:16:17.026+09:00">讲的是远近、险易、宽窄和死地生地等地理形势。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:16:25.544+09:00">所谓将帅，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:16:42.897+09:00">讲的是才智、诚信、仁爱、勇敢、严明等基本素质。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:17:05.711+09:00">所谓法制，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:17:25.824+09:00">讲的是军务法度、军需军用物质的掌管、使用制度。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:17:33.698+09:00">以上五大方面的情况，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:18:01.945+09:00">将帅都必须了然千心，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:18:15.54+09:00">了解这些情况就会获胜，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.26" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:18:25.786+09:00">不了解就不能获胜。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.27" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:18:34.61+09:00">所以，比较敌我形势，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.28" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:18:46.354+09:00">探索战争胜负要考察七个方面，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:18:52.4+09:00">即：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.30" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:19:02.967+09:00">哪一方的国君政治比较开明？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:19:14.433+09:00">哪一方的将帅比较善千带兵用兵？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:19:38.183+09:00">哪一方得了天时、地利之便？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:19:46.892+09:00">哪一方比较能始终贯彻执行严明的法令？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:19:52.978+09:00">哪一方的军事综合力量比较强大？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:20:00.312+09:00">哪一方的士卒比较训练有素？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.36" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:20:10.661+09:00">哪一方的赏罚比较公正严明？</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3b0003_tls_001-2a.37" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-13T17:20:13.039+09:00">根据以上的对比，就可以判断出谁胜谁负了。</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
